<h2>Welcome to SDK Admin Portal!</h2>

<p>Hello {{name}},</p>

<p>You have been invited to join the SDK Admin Portal. An administrator has created an account for you with the following details:</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3>Account Information</h3>
    <table class="info-table">
        <tr>
            <td>Email Address:</td>
            <td>{{email}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Temporary Password:</td>
            <td><code style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #495057; letter-spacing: 2px;">{{temporaryPassword}}</code></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Role:</td>
            <td>{{role}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Status:</td>
            <td>{{status}}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>

<div class="alert alert-warning">
    <p><strong>Important:</strong> For security reasons, you will be required to change this password when you first log in.</p>
</div>

<div class="alert alert-info">
    <h4>How to Access Your Account</h4>
    <ol>
        <li>Visit the SDK Admin Portal login page</li>
        <li>Enter your email address and the temporary password above</li>
        <li>You will be prompted to change your password immediately</li>
        <li>Complete your profile setup</li>
    </ol>
</div>

<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact your system administrator.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
<strong>SDK Admin Portal Team</strong></p> 